!!!
%html
  %body
    .span15
      .container
        .col-md-12
          .row
            .page-header
              %h1
                Static Wordlists
            .row
              .col-md-10.pull-left
                Wordlists are used in dictionary attacks. Hashview comes preloaded with one wordlist, but you can upload more by clicking the 'Upload Wordlist' button to the left or by dropping the files to /[install path]/control/wordlists/.
              .col-md-2.pull-right
                %a.btn.btn-primary.pull-right{href: '/wordlists/add'}
                  Upload Wordlist
      %br
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-12
            .table
              %table{class: 'table table-striped'}
                %thead
                  %tr
                    %th
                      %b Name
                    %th
                      %b Size
                    %th
                      %b Action
                %tbody
                  - if @static_wordlists
                    - @static_wordlists.each do |wordlist|
                      %tr
                        %td #{wordlist.name}
                        %td #{wordlist.size}
                        %td
                          %a.btn.btn-info{href: "#modal-wordlist-#{wordlist.id}-info", "data-toggle" => 'modal'}
                            %i.glyphicon.glyphicon-info-sign{title: 'Info'}
                          .modal.fade.modal{id: "modal-wordlist-#{wordlist.id}-info", role: 'dialog', tabindex: '-1', "aria-hidden" => 'true'}
                            .modal-dialog.modal-lg
                              .modal-content
                                .modal-header
                                  %button.close{'aria-label' => 'Close', 'data-dismiss' => 'modal', type: 'button'}
                                    %span{'aria-hidden' => 'true'} &times;
                                  %h4.modal-title Details for #{wordlist.name}
                                .modal-body
                                  %p
                                    The following tasks are using this wordlist.
                                  .table
                                    %table{class: 'table table-striped'}
                                      - if @tasks
                                        - @tasks.each do |task|
                                          - if task.wl_id.to_i == wordlist.id.to_i
                                            %tr
                                              %td #{task.name}
                                      - else
                                        No task is using this wordlist
                                  %p
                                .modal-footer
                                  %button.btn.btn-default{"data-dismiss" => "modal", type: 'button'} Close
                          %a.btn.btn-danger{href: "/wordlists/delete/#{wordlist.id}"}
                            %i.glyphicon.glyphicon-trash{title: 'Delete'}
      .container
        .row
          .page-header
            %h1
              Dynamic Wordlists
        .row
          .col-md-10.pull-left
            Dynamic Wordlists are automatically generated by Hashview. They contain the plaintext passwords collected by other cracked hashfiles. They can be used in tasks with rules just like static wordlists
      %br
      %br
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-12
            .table
              %table{class: 'table table-striped'}
                %thead
                  %tr
                    %th
                      %b Name
                    %th
                      %b Size
                %tbody
                  - if @dynamic_wordlists
                    - @dynamic_wordlists.each do |wordlist|
                      %tr
                        %td #{wordlist.name}
                        %td #{wordlist.size}
